nodes.text: Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.33

Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.33 is the thirty-third issue of the 6th volume of Star Wars Comic UK, published on May 3, 2012. The magazine includes the feature Top 5 Fighters, the Episode Guide to "A Friend in Need," and a free gift, the Bounty Hunter Secret Snare. This is a Lego Star Wars Takeover Issue.
The comic included the comic strip "A Small Scrappy War!"
Two free gifts, stickers and a Wrist Launcher, come with this issue.
